                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>New York</placeName>\n                <date>July 5/58</date>\n            </p>\n            <p>My dear <addressee>Mr Leeser</addressee></p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">The Occident for<lb/>\n                <date>June</date> &amp; <date>July</date> came safely &amp; duly<lb/> to hand and\n                have been distributed<lb/> to your subscribers, excepting <persName>P\n                    Haas</persName><lb/>\n                <persName>N Myers</persName>\n                <persName>Mansfild</persName> &amp; Thro <persName>A.<lb/> Meyer</persName>, whose\n                address I cannot ascer<lb/>tain. Please note the address of the<lb/> following.\n                    <persName>M. N. Lichtunstien</persName>\n                <placeName>98 West 22nd<lb/> Street</placeName>. <persName>L. M.\n                    Ritterband</persName>\n                <placeName>224. Bowery</placeName><lb/>\n                <persName>Mrs R. Rehine</persName>\n                <placeName>196 West 15th Street</placeName> and<lb/>\n                <persName>Julius Abecaris</persName>\n                <placeName>101 Wall St</placeName> for your<lb/> guidance.</p>\n            <p><persName>Mr L. Arnold</persName> has left with me</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3t14v883/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
