                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>a list of names who he says had<lb/> each a copy of your Bible. They are</p>\n            <table cols=\"2\" rows=\"9\">\n                <row>\n                    <cell>\n                        <persName>Morris Wilson</persName>\n                    </cell>\n                    <cell>$9</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>\n                        <persName>B. Solomon</persName>\n                    </cell>\n                    <cell> 9</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>\n                        <persName>Rowland Davis</persName>\n                    </cell>\n                    <cell> 9</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>\n                        <persName>David J Levy &amp; Bro</persName>\n                    </cell>\n                    <cell> 9</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>\n                        <persName>Asher Rosenblatt</persName>\n                    </cell>\n                    <cell> 9</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>\n                        <persName>John M. Davis</persName>\n                    </cell>\n                    <cell> 9</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>\n                        <persName>L. Mack</persName>\n                    </cell>\n                    <cell> 8</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>\n                        <persName>B. Cohen</persName>\n                    </cell>\n                    <cell> 9</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>\n                        <persName>Aaron Jacob</persName>\n                    </cell>\n                    <cell> 9</cell>\n                </row>\n            </table>\n            <p>I have done nothing towards<lb/> collecting any of these, thinking<lb/> you would be\n                here yourself<lb/> before this time, and that you<lb/> could do it much more\n                satisfac-<lb/>torily than I could</p>\n            <p>With love to <persName>Mrs Cozens</persName> &amp; the young ladies.<lb/> Believe me\n                as ever your sincere friend &amp; well wisher</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(11)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">Hanford</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p>PS. My niece has arrived from<lb/>\n                <placeName>Mobile</placeName> and is duly installed in<lb/> my family, besides this\n                    <persName>Mrs Hanford</persName><lb/> expects to be confined early in\n                    <date>Augt</date><lb/> so you see I am rapidly getting both<lb/> my hands &amp;\n                my house full</p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3t14v883/canvas/p2"
                }
